				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-check"></i>Features</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Create personal profiles.</li>
					<li>Connect with friends and colleagues.</li>
					<li>Share comments, photos, files and folders.</li>
					<li>All shareable applications have a Share menu on the top menu bar.</li>
					<li>All shareable applications can access your social network.</li>
					<li>The file system and social network are integrated making it easy to share your files with your friends and colleagues.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

